      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoI directly maps to clinically reported hemolysis metric (plasma free hemoglobin); sensitivity of NIH to model parameters documented.",
      "rationale": "NIH is the standard clinical surrogate; mapping to plasma free hemoglobin is established in literature. Sensitivity analysis performed for two of six key parameters. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
    },
