      "rationale": "No independent review of CFD setup parameters performed. Boundary condition selection and turbulence model choice not peer-reviewed. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive law selection justified by sensitivity studies; alternative model forms evaluated.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected without comparative evaluation against LES or other RANS closures. Hemolysis power-law exponents taken from literature without local calibration. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
