      "rationale": "Monte Carlo framework was scoped in the analysis plan but not executed. Input distributions for hemolysis model coefficients are undocumented. No confidence intervals on NIH predictions available. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 5."
